</head>
<body> <nav> <div class="container"> <div class="logo-group"> <div class="logo-mark"> <a href="#" class="logo">REIGNITE</a><span class="logo-dot">.</span> </div> <span class="logo-sub">Advisors</span> </div> <a href="https://reignite-rrrcbwwi.scoreapp.com/" class="btn btn-gold nav-cta" target="_blank"><i class="fas fa-calendar-check"></i> Apply for Private Advisory</a> </div> </nav> <section class="hero"> <div class="hero-left"> <div class="hero-tag">Your Experience</div> <h1>Turn What You Already Know Into a Sellable Intellectual Asset</h1> <p class="hero-sub">A private architecture engagement for experienced professionals ready to turn lived expertise into structured offers for a defined audience</p>
  <p class="hero-sub" style="margin-top: 16px; color: var(--gold-light); font-weight: 600;">No courses. No guesswork. No trading time for money.</p>
</p> <div class="hero-ctas"> <a href="https://reignite-rrrcbwwi.scoreapp.com/" class="btn btn-gold" target="_blank"> <i class="fas fa-compass"></i> Apply for Private Advisory </a> <span class="micro-assurance">Limited private slots each month. Qualified applicants only.</span> </div> </div> <div class="hero-right"> <div class="hero-image-wrapper"> <img src="steven-headshot-transparent.png" alt="Steven Tshakatumba"> </div> <div class="hero-wordmark">REIGNITE</div> </div> </section> <section class="trust-strip"> <div class="container"> <p>Trusted by current and former executives and leaders across Fortune 500 and high-growth organizations, including:</p> <div class="trust-marquee"> <div class="trust-logos" aria-label="Trust logos"><div class="trust-logo"><img src="/steven/logo-tsx.png?v=12" alt="TSX"></div>
<div class="trust-logo"><img src="/steven/logo-kpmg.png?v=12" alt="KPMG"></div>
<div class="trust-logo"><img src="/steven/logo-stradig.png?v=12" alt="Stradig"></div>
<div class="trust-logo"><img src="/steven/logo-whycoach.png?v=12" alt="WHY Coach"></div>
<div class="trust-logo"><img src="/steven/logo-salesforce.png?v=12" alt="Salesforce"></div>
<div class="trust-logo"><img src="/steven/logo-1.png?v=12" alt="Reignite"></div>
<div class="trust-logo"><img src="/steven/logo-tsx.png?v=12" alt="TSX"></div>
<div class="trust-logo"><img src="/steven/logo-kpmg.png?v=12" alt="KPMG"></div>
<div class="trust-logo"><img src="/steven/logo-stradig.png?v=12" alt="Stradig"></div>
<div class="trust-logo"><img src="/steven/logo-whycoach.png?v=12" alt="WHY Coach"></div>
<div class="trust-logo"><img src="/steven/logo-salesforce.png?v=12" alt="Salesforce"></div>
<div class="trust-logo"><img src="/steven/logo-1.png?v=12" alt="Reignite"></div></div> </div> </section> <section class="why"> <div class="container">
<h2>You’re here because…</h2>
<ul class="why-bullets">
  <li>You’ve spent years solving real problems, yet your value feels under-monetized.</li>
  <li>You can explain what you know, but struggle to sell it.</li>
  <li>You’re tired of trading hours for income.</li>
  <li>You want leverage, legacy, and impact.</li>
</ul>
 <h2>The Problem Isn't Experience - <span>It's Packaging</span></h2>
<h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 20px;">Here’s the truth about your experience</h2>
<p class="section-sub" style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 25px;">Most professionals think value only exists as a job title, resume or hourly consulting. But real value lives in:</p> <ul class="why-bullets"> <li>Unclear positioning <span>→</span> weak demand</li> <li>Offer sprawl <span>→</span> low conversion</li> <li>Time-for-money <span>→</span> no leverage</li> </ul> <div class="why-grid"> <div class="why-card why-card-left"> <h3>What you have now</h3> <ul> <li>Deep expertise</li> <li>Hourly calls</li> <li>Invisible to ideal clients</li> </ul> </div> <div class="why-card why-card-right"> <h3>What REIGNITE<span class="tm">™</span> delivers</h3> <ul> <li>Clearly defined strategic advisory asset</li> <li>Premium fixed-fee offers</li> <li>A repeatable path to high-value clients</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </section> <!-- Anti-Pattern Stack -->
<section class="anti-pattern">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>You've Probably Tried…</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Common approaches that keep you stuck in the advisory trap.</p>
    <div class="anti-pattern-stack">
      <div class="anti-pattern-row">
        <i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i>
        <span>Free advice on LinkedIn</span>
      </div>
      <div class="anti-pattern-row">
        <i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i>
        <span>Generic courses that don't fit your context</span>
      </div>
      <div class="anti-pattern-row">
        <i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i>
        <span>Pricing guesswork</span>
      </div>
      <div class="anti-pattern-row">
        <i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i>
        <span>Hourly consulting with no leverage</span>
      </div>
    </div>
<div class="anti-pattern-transition" style="margin-top: 18px; font-style: normal;">But none of this actually…</div>
<div class="anti-pattern-stack" style="margin-top: 12px;">
  <div class="anti-pattern-row"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <span>Defines your real asset</span></div>
