<section class="momentum-triangle"> <div class="container"> <h2>The REIGNITE<span class="tm">™</span> <span>Momentum Triangle</span></h2> <p class="section-sub">When Clarity, Offer, and Demand are engineered together, your advisory business builds compounding momentum.</p> <div class="triangle-wrap"> <div class="triangle-core"> <svg class="triangle-lines" viewBox="0 0 420 300" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true"> <path d="M210 26L56 293H364L210 26Z"/> <path class="triangle-accent" d="M210 26L56 293H364L210 26Z"/> </svg> <div class="triangle-flow-dot" aria-hidden="true"></div> <div class="triangle-flow-dot dot-2" aria-hidden="true"></div> <div class="triangle-node clarity" aria-hidden="true"><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i></div> <div class="triangle-node offer" aria-hidden="true"><i class="fas fa-gem"></i></div> <div class="triangle-node demand" aria-hidden="true"><i class="fas fa-bullhorn"></i></div> <div class="triangle-label clarity">Clarity</div> <div class="triangle-label offer">Offer</div> <div class="triangle-label demand">Demand</div> <div class="triangle-center">Momentum</div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class="framework" id="architecture"><div class="container"><h2>Private Engagement</h2><p class="section-sub">REIGNITE is delivered as a private architecture engagement. This is selective work designed for experienced professionals ready to build leverage, not experiment.</p><div class="framework-image-placeholder" style="max-width: 920px; margin: 0 auto 40px;"><div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px dashed rgba(201,168,76,0.45); border-radius: 12px; padding: 38px 24px; text-align: center; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);">PLACEHOLDER IMAGE — REIGNITE Architecture Process Visual (to be designed)</div></div><h2 style="font-size: 1.6rem; margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Engagement Includes</h2><h2>The REIGNITE<span class="tm">™</span> <span>Architecture Process</span></h2> <p class="section-sub">A private, proven 6-step system that extracts your deepest executive expertise and transforms it into a premium, scalable intellectual asset — one that generates revenue and impact without requiring your constant time.</p> <div class="framework-pathway-desktop"> <div class="framework-step"> <div class="framework-step-head"> <div class="framework-step-icon"><i class="fas fa-magnifying-glass"></i></div> </div> <h4>Reveal</h4> <div class="framework-step-divider"></div> <p>Surface the highest-value insight buried in your experience.</p> </div> <div class="framework-step"> <div class="framework-step-head"> <div class="framework-step-icon"><i class="fas fa-gem"></i></div> </div> <h4>Crystallize</h4> <div class="framework-step-divider"></div> <p>Shape a distinctive method clients can trust and buy.</p> </div> <div class="framework-step"> <div class="framework-step-head"> <div class="framework-step-icon"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i></div> </div> <h4>Align</h4> <div class="framework-step-divider"></div> <p>Define the exact clients who pay premium for this work.</p> </div> <div class="framework-step"> <div class="framework-step-head"> <div class="framework-step-icon"><i class="fas fa-drafting-compass"></i></div> </div> <h4>Architect</h4> <div class="framework-step-divider"></div> <p>Build one flagship offer that scales beyond hourly work.</p> </div> <div class="framework-step"> <div class="framework-step-head"> <div class="framework-step-icon"><i class="fas fa-book-open"></i></div> </div> <h4>Codify</h4> <div class="framework-step-divider"></div> <p>Package it into an asset that delivers without constant involvement.</p> </div> <div class="framework-step"> <div class="framework-step-head"> <div class="framework-step-icon"><i class="fas fa-fire"></i></div> </div> <h4>Ignite</h4> <div class="framework-step-divider"></div> <p>Launch with precision and create immediate market momentum.</p> </div> </div> <span class="framework-connector c1">➜</span> <span class="framework-connector c2">➜</span> <span class="framework-connector c3">➜</span> <span class="framework-connector c4">➜</span> <div class="framework-pathway-mobile"> <div class="framework-stage"> <div class="framework-stage-head"> <div class="framework-step-mobile-icon"><i class="fas fa-magnifying-glass"></i></div> </div> <div class="framework-stage-content"> <h4>Reveal</h4> <p>Surface the highest-value insight buried in your experience.</p> </div> </div> <div class="framework-stage"> <div class="framework-stage-head"> <div class="framework-step-mobile-icon"><i class="fas fa-gem"></i></div> </div> <div class="framework-stage-content"> <h4>Crystallize</h4> <p>Shape a distinctive method clients can trust and buy.</p> </div> </div> <div class="framework-stage"> <div class="framework-stage-head"> <div class="framework-step-mobile-icon"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i></div> </div> <div class="framework-stage-content"> <h4>Align</h4> <p>Define the exact clients who pay premium for this work.</p> </div> </div> <div class="framework-stage"> <div class="framework-stage-head"> <div class="framework-step-mobile-icon"><i class="fas fa-drafting-compass"></i></div> </div> <div class="framework-stage-content"> <h4>Architect</h4> <p>Build one flagship offer that scales beyond hourly work.</p> </div> </div> <div class="framework-stage"> <div class="framework-stage-head"> <div class="framework-step-mobile-icon"><i class="fas fa-book-open"></i></div> </div> <div class="framework-stage-content"> <h4>Codify</h4> <p>Package it into an asset that delivers without constant involvement.</p> </div> </div> <div class="framework-stage"> <div class="framework-stage-head"> <div class="framework-step-mobile-icon"><i class="fas fa-fire"></i></div> </div> <div class="framework-stage-content"> <h4>Ignite</h4> <p>Launch with precision and create immediate market momentum.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <!-- Contrast Matrix --> <section class="contrast-matrix"> <div class="container"> <h2>What REIGNITE<span class="tm">™</span> <span>Delivers</span></h2> <p class="section-sub">The difference between struggling to monetize and building a scalable asset.</p> <div class="matrix-container"> <div class="matrix-header"> <div class="matrix-header-left">Typical Approach</div> <div class="matrix-header-right">REIGNITE<span class="tm">™</span> Approach</div> </div> <div class="matrix-row"> <div class="matrix-row-left"> <i class="fas fa-minus"></i> <span>Vague expertise</span> </div> <div class="matrix-row-right"> <i class="fas fa-check"></i> <span>Clearly defined strategic advisory asset</span> </div> </div> <div class="matrix-row"> <div class="matrix-row-left"> <i class="fas fa-minus"></i> <span>Broad audience</span> </div> <div class="matrix-row-right"> <i class="fas fa-check"></i> <span>Precise buyer profile</span> </div> </div> <div class="matrix-row"> <div class="matrix-row-left"> <i class="fas fa-minus"></i> <span>Inconsistent services</span> </div> <div class="matrix-row-right"> <i class="fas fa-check"></i> <span>Structured sellable offer</span> </div> </div> <div class="matrix-row"> <div class="matrix-row-left"> <i class="fas fa-minus"></i> <span>Time-for-money</span> </div> <div class="matrix-row-right"> <i class="fas fa-check"></i> <span>Scalable advisory model</span> </div> </div> <div class="matrix-cta"> <a href="https://reignite-rrrcbwwi.scoreapp.com/" class="btn btn-gold"> <i class="fas fa-calendar-check"></i> Apply for Private Advisory </a> <span class="micro-assurance">Limited private slots each month. Qualified applicants only.</span> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class="results"> <div class="container"> <h2>Client <span>Proof</span></h2> <p class="section-sub">What clients said before and after tightening their positioning and execution with Reignite.</p>

